The Content Bounty API makes it easy to save any data you want into the database, and to retreive it
later.

Step 1:		Make sure your class extends BaseComponent.  There are many examples of this in the project so details on how
to do this are not provided here.  Just do a search for "extends BaseComponent"

Step 2:		Base sure you include an instance of BaseService in the extended BaseComponent.  This is also frequently done...
but it's not a requirement so be sure to check for this.

